Download the code
You will have to install NodeJS
run npm install
migrate the schema.sql file placed in the config folder (this will get the Database ready)

you can then go to http://localhost:8080/api/login
Enter the email as vamsi.bulusu@rutgers.edu and password as vamsi123

this should take you to the HomePage

The Homepage has a logout button, on pressing which you will be logged out and redirected to the login page

Our registration functionality is also working, you can create a new user and login using that as well

Routes for your convenience:
- API Documentation
    * GET - /api/login - login page
    * POST - /api/login - Home page
    * GET - /api/register -> register page
    * POST - /api/register -> login page